msgstr "The token could not be checked due to a network error. Check your internet connection and try again."

#: controller/main_controller.py:389
msgid "El token no es válido. Comprueba que lo copiaste completo desde el portal de desarrolladores de Discord."
msgstr "The token is not valid. Make sure you copied it in full from the Discord developer portal."
